    <description># RELEASE PATCH

## General:
* All inventories will be cleared before release. **Gp will remain.**
* The armor shop now has 3 price tiers: 750, 1250, 1500
* The weapon shop now has 4 price tiers: 750, 1250, 1500, 2000
* New weapon called Ceremonial Blood Staff.
* Voidstone of Corax weapon now has an aura on the hand that will be visible during the day. The execution animation has also been updated.
* You now earn 75 gold when winning a game, and 45 when losing (up from 50/35).
* Backer-exclusive items are now hidden to all. They will return to backers only soon!
* New players now start with 500gp (upped from 300)

## Bug Fixes:
* Priest should be fixed.
* Fixed tutorial buttons not resetting
* Friends list fixes
* Bloaty log fixes
* Some others.</description>
    
